            <h3 style="margin-top:18px;"><span class="lang-only-en">Web Design</span><span class="lang-only-es">Diseño Web</span></h3>
            <p style="font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0 0 12px;"><span class="lang-only-en">Modern, responsive, SEO-optimized websites that convert visitors into customers and strengthen your brand authority across South Florida.</span><span class="lang-only-es">Sitios web modernos, responsivos y optimizados para SEO que convierten visitantes en clientes y fortalecen la autoridad de tu marca en todo el Sur de Florida.</span></p>
            <span class="more"><span class="lang-only-en">See More</span><span class="lang-only-es">Ver Más</span></span>
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="card-border is-cyan">
          <a class="card-glass service-link" href="/services/digital-marketing">
            <span class="svc-icon is-cyan"><img src="/images/Marketing-Icon.svg" alt=""></span>
            <h3 style="margin-top:18px;"><span class="lang-only-en">Digital Marketing</span><span class="lang-only-es">Marketing Digital</span></h3>
            <p style="font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0 0 12px;"><span class="lang-only-en">SEO, Google Ads, and data-driven marketing strategies that attract qualified traffic and generate leads for local businesses.</span><span class="lang-only-es">SEO, Google Ads y estrategias de marketing basadas en datos que atraen tráfico calificado y generan prospectos para negocios locales.</span></p>
            <span class="more"><span class="lang-only-en">See More</span><span class="lang-only-es">Ver Más</span></span>
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="card-border is-green">
          <a class="card-glass service-link" href="/services/web-development">
            <span class="svc-icon is-green"><img src="/images/Development-Icon.svg" alt=""></span>
