        </div>
        <div class="grid-4" data-reveal-children>
          <article class="process-block">
            <img class="process-img" src="/images/process/explore.avif" alt="Digital strategy and market discovery for South Florida businesses" loading="lazy">
            <div class="process-glass"></div>
            <div class="process-content">
              <div class="process-header">
                <h3><span class="lang-only-en">1. Explore</span><span class="lang-only-es">1. Explorar</span></h3>
                <h4><span class="lang-only-en">Digital Strategy &amp; Market Discovery</span><span class="lang-only-es">Estrategia Digital y Descubrimiento de Mercado</span></h4>
              </div>
              <p><span class="lang-only-en">We analyze goals, audience, and market to uncover growth opportunities across South Florida.</span><span class="lang-only-es">Analizamos metas, audiencia y mercado para descubrir oportunidades de crecimiento en todo el Sur de Florida.</span></p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="process-block">
            <img class="process-img" src="/images/process/estimate.avif" alt="Project planning and strategic roadmap for a web project" loading="lazy">
            <div class="process-glass"></div>
            <div class="process-content">
              <div class="process-header">
                <h3><span class="lang-only-en">2. Estimate</span><span class="lang-only-es">2. Estimar</span></h3>
                <h4><span class="lang-only-en">Project Planning &amp; Strategic Roadmap</span><span class="lang-only-es">Planificación del Proyecto y Hoja de Ruta Estratégica</span></h4>
              </div>
