            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="process-block">
            <img class="process-img" src="/images/process/development.avif" alt="Custom web development and SEO build in progress" loading="lazy">
            <div class="process-glass"></div>
            <div class="process-content">
              <div class="process-header">
                <h3><span class="lang-only-en">3. Development</span><span class="lang-only-es">3. Desarrollo</span></h3>
                <h4><span class="lang-only-en">Custom Web Development &amp; SEO</span><span class="lang-only-es">Desarrollo Web a la Medida y SEO</span></h4>
              </div>
              <p><span class="lang-only-en">We build high-performance websites and platforms optimized for SEO and conversions.</span><span class="lang-only-es">Construimos sitios web y plataformas de alto rendimiento optimizados para SEO y conversiones.</span></p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="process-block">
            <img class="process-img" src="/images/process/delivery.avif" alt="Website launch and ongoing optimization in Plantation, FL" loading="lazy">
            <div class="process-glass"></div>
            <div class="process-content">
              <div class="process-header">
                <h3><span class="lang-only-en">4. Delivery</span><span class="lang-only-es">4. Entrega</span></h3>
                <h4><span class="lang-only-en">Website Launch &amp; Ongoing Optimization</span><span class="lang-only-es">Lanzamiento del Sitio y Optimización Continua</span></h4>
              </div>
              <p><span class="lang-only-en">We launch and optimize your digital presence from Plantation, serving South Florida.</span><span class="lang-only-es">Lanzamos y optimizamos tu presencia digital desde Plantation, al servicio del Sur de Florida.</span></p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="center-cta" style="margin-top: 3rem;" data-reveal>
          <a href="#" class="btn" onclick="if(window.Calendly){Calendly.initPopupWidget({url:'https://calendly.com/leads-senaviacorp/30-minute-meeting-clon'});}return false;"><span class="lang-only-en">Book a Free Call</span><span class="lang-only-es">Agenda tu Llamada Gratis</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

